@0 = ~Aye? I've little enough stock left... and barely enough metal t' forge. State yer business or move on.~
@1 = ~What sells you?~
@2 = ~Can I see what you have?~
@3 = ~Can I ask you questions?~
@4 = ~Goodbye.~
@5 = ~I used to have one of the finest armories in Luskan. As it is, I've been forced to set up shop here with a... rudimentary stock. I'll sell what I has, though, before them thugs come an' take it from me o'er my dead body.~ /*I used to have one of the finest armories in Luskan. As it is, I've been forced to set up shop here with a... rudimentary stock.*/
@6 = ~Aye. Ye can look but ye can't touch... 'tis all of the finest manufacture.~
@7 = ~I be not in the mood to answer your questions. Find someone else t' bother, if ye not be a paying customer.~
@8 = ~Aye, then, off ye go an' leave me be.~
